    segment_marche,
    SEGMENT_RECHARGE,

        WHEN DAY(DATE_LOADED) BETWEEN 1 AND 10 THEN 'Beginning of Month'
        WHEN DAY(DATE_LOADED) BETWEEN 11 AND 20 THEN 'Middle of Month'
        ELSE 'End of Month'
    END AS subscription_period,

Quel est le CA data, recharge, voix par marché sur le T1 2025

Requête SQL générée :

SELECT
    rcdm.year AS annee,
    rcdm.month AS mois,
    rcdm.segment_marche AS marche,
    SUM(rcdm.ca_data) AS total_data_revenue,
    SUM(rrdx.ca_recharge_global) AS total_recharge_revenue,
    SUM((
        CASE
            WHEN rcdm.segment_marche = rrdx.segment_marche THEN rrdx.ca_recharge_global
            ELSE 0
        END
    )) AS total_recharge_revenue_matched,
    SUM(rmv.orange + rmv.free + rmv.promobile + rmv.csu_mobile + rmv.divv + rmv.expresso_mobile + rmv.fixe_expresso + rmv.fixe_sonatel + rmv.international + rmv.ci_pass_dur + rmv.cy_pass_dur + rmv.cy_gratuit_dur + rmv.cp_dur + rmv.cb_dur) AS total_voice_revenue
FROM
    reporting_ca_data_monthly AS rcdm
LEFT JOIN
    reporting_recharge_daily_xarre AS rrdx ON rcdm.year = rrdx.year AND rcdm.month = rrdx.month AND rcdm.segment_marche = rrdx.segment_marche
LEFT JOIN
    reporting_monthly_voix AS rmv ON rcdm.year = rmv.year AND rcdm.month = rmv.month AND rcdm.segment_marche = rmv.segment_marche
WHERE
    rcdm.year = 2025
    AND rcdm.month IN (1, 2, 3)
GROUP BY
    rcdm.year,
    rcdm.month,
    rcdm.segment_marche
ORDER BY
    rcdm.segment_marche,
    rcdm.month;

fait moi la segmentation des clients selon leur usage en data, voix ou mixte

Requête SQL générée :

SELECT
    cu.MSISDN AS client_id,
    cu.year AS annee,
    cu.month AS mois,
    CASE
        WHEN COALESCE(SUM(cu.data_volume), 0) > 0 AND COALESCE(SUM(cu.voice_duration), 0) = 0 THEN 'Data User'
        WHEN COALESCE(SUM(cu.voice_duration), 0) > 0 AND COALESCE(SUM(cu.data_volume), 0) = 0 THEN 'Voice User'
        WHEN COALESCE(SUM(cu.data_volume), 0) > 0 AND COALESCE(SUM(cu.voice_duration), 0) > 0 THEN 'Mixed User'
        ELSE 'No Usage Recorded' -- Catégorie pour les clients sans usage data ou voix enregistré pour le mois
    END AS usage_segment
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            md.MSISDN,
            md.year,
            md.month,
            md.total_volume_mo AS data_volume,
            0 AS voice_duration
        FROM
            monthly_data AS md
        WHERE
            md.year = 2025 -- Filtrer pour l'année en cours (2025) comme spécifié
        UNION ALL
        SELECT
            mv.MSISDN,
            mv.year,
            mv.month,
            0 AS data_volume,
            mv.cb_dur AS voice_duration
        FROM
            monthly_voix AS mv
        WHERE
            mv.year = 2025 -- Filtrer pour l'année en cours (2025) comme spécifié
    ) AS cu
GROUP BY
    cu.MSISDN,
    cu.year,
    cu.month
ORDER BY
    cu.year DESC,
    cu.month DESC,
    client_id ASC;
Donne moi le volume d’appels par commune pour les clients Mass-Market

Requête SQL générée :

SELECT
    rmv.year AS year,
    rmv.month AS month,
    rmv.ca_cr_commune AS commune,
    SUM(rmv.Orange) AS volume_appels
FROM
    reporting_monthly_voix AS rmv
WHERE
    rmv.SEGMENT_RECHARGE LIKE '%Mass-Market%'
    AND rmv.year = 2025 -- Filtrer pour l'année en cours (2025)
GROUP BY
    rmv.year,
    rmv.month,
    rmv.ca_cr_commune
ORDER BY
    rmv.year DESC,
    rmv.month DESC,
    volume_appels DESC;
